title: Karolyn James - Chasing Cross Series
description:
Karolyn James, Chasing Cross book series

A great series featuring different members of a rock band, Chasing Cross. I've only read the first and half of the second book so far, but who doesn't love romance and rock??

I got the first book free from Amazon, and couldn't find the others anywhere on this site. It's a great series, so I had to look around and find them. I hope you enjoy! The books included are in epub form and include:

All Access
Broken Sound
Bitter Farewell
Buried Notes
Last Song

I really hope you enjoy and I look forward to uploading more book series that I've enjoyed!
